    It's easy and common that people getting trapped into all kinds of thoughts.According to a research conducted by Harvard
University,our minds are lost in thoughts almost 47 percent of the time on average which also caused the unhappiness of our
life.
    In order to deal with that,all you need is to take 10 mindful minutes which helps you to step back and get a different 
